Text:
@reflexes did you run the Skidrow.exe after copying it (and the rest of the skidrow contents) into the game directory where it was installed? It will run a screen and unlock the game. Wont work otherwise.

This is what I did and it worked perfectly. No issues. If it isn't working you are doing it wrong! Go and buy the full version if you can't figure it out. Good luck!

PS- Game is very short. only about 8-9 hours to go through it.
